<materialsCitation id="61F1F00F1B0DFFC1F7BFF642F5E4F5AF" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3798388316" pageId="19" pageNumber="530">“La Puntilla, near Tinogasta, Catamarca,” 28°04’ S, 67°34’ W, at ¢.1000 m, Argentina</materialsCitation>
